'''2016年卡拉馬祖枪击案'''為發生在[[美東時間|美東時間]]2016年2月20日於[[美国|美国]][[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[卡拉馬祖縣|卡拉馬祖縣]]的一起连环枪击案，此事件造成6人死亡，2人受伤，而警方已將嫌犯拘捕<ref name="cnn">{{citeweb|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/02/21/us/michigan-kalamazoo-county-shooting-spree/|title=7 dead in Kalamazoo County shooting spree; suspect in custody|author=Joshua Berlinger and Joe Sutton, CNN|date=21 February 2016|work=CNN|accessdate=21 February 2016|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222094736/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/02/21/us/michigan-kalamazoo-county-shooting-spree/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sinclairbroadcastgroup">{{cite web|url=http://wwmt.com/news/local/search-for-suspect-after-multiple-fatal-shootings|title=UPDATE: Fifth Cracker Barrel shooting victim dies, bringing toll to 7|author=Sinclair Broadcast Group|work=WWMT|accessdate=2016-02-21|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222080800/http://wwmt.com/news/local/search-for-suspect-after-multiple-fatal-shootings|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nytimes">{{citeweb|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/22/us/kalamazoo-michigan-random-shootings.html|title=Gunman Kills at Least 7 in Michigan|date=22 February 2016|work=The New York Times|accessdate=21 February 2016|archive-date=2016-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221123418/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/22/us/kalamazoo-michigan-random-shootings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==槍擊案==
美東時間2月20日傍晚5時45分，嫌犯先在[[卡拉马祖_(密歇根州)|卡拉马祖]]的一處公寓停車場朝一名女子開槍，該名女子身受重傷，生命垂危<ref name=HallMLive/><ref name="woodtv-police-id">{{cite news |title= 6 Killed, 2 Injured After Kalamazoo-Area Shooting Spree |url= http://woodtv.com/2016/02/20/multiple-fatally-shot-at-2-locations-in-kalamazoo-co/ |location= Grand Rapids, MI |publisher= [[WOOD-TV|WOOD-TV]] |date= February 20, 2016 |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-02-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160221215651/http://woodtv.com/2016/02/20/multiple-fatally-shot-at-2-locations-in-kalamazoo-co/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="fox17">{{cite news |title= 6 Dead in Kalamazoo County Shootings: Suspect Arrested |url= http://fox17online.com/2016/02/20/police-man-randomly-shooting-in-kalamazoo-co-dead/?utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter_FOX17 |location= Grand Rapids, MI |publisher= [[WXMI-TV|WXMI-TV]] |agency= [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date= February 20, 2016 |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160311095535/http://fox17online.com/2016/02/20/police-man-randomly-shooting-in-kalamazoo-co-dead/?utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter_FOX17 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=WhyToday>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2016/02/21/reports-gunman-kills-least-6-michigan/80694468/|title=After Kalamazoo shootings, the big question: Why?|work=USA Today|date=February 21, 2016|accessdate=February 21, 2016|first=Katrease|last=Stafford|archive-date=2016-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160226075715/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2016/02/21/reports-gunman-kills-least-6-michigan/80694468/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大約三小時後，嫌犯到達於[[卡拉马祖_(密歇根州)|卡拉马祖]]的[[起亚汽车|起亚汽车]]經銷商停車場後朝3名被害人開槍，造成2人死亡；後來又到{{le|德克薩斯查特鎮區 (密歇根州)|Texas Charter Township, Michigan|德克薩斯查特鎮區}}的餅乾桶餐廳（Cracker Barrel）停車場朝兩台車共4名被害人開槍，造成車內4人死亡，1人受傷<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ew0oRK3blLQ |title= Live At Cracker Barrel |location= Kalamazoo, MI |publisher= WWMT-TV |date= February 21, 2016 |via= [[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate= 2016-03-04 |archive-date= 2019-02-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190214150300/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ew0oRK3blLQ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=NBC/> 。

== 嫌犯 ==
警方確認出這起槍擊案嫌犯為45歲男子賈森·道爾頓（Jason Dalton）。警方於當地時間21日凌晨12時40分將嫌犯拘捕，並且查扣他的黑色{{le|雪佛蘭HHR|Chevy HHR}}汽車，這款車於此槍擊案中與逃走車輛的描述吻合。警方在他車上搜出一把[[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]<ref name="woodtv-police-id"/>。警方表示這名嫌犯並無任何犯罪前科<ref>[http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/latest-police-id-suspect-fatal-michigan-shootings-37093030 The Latest: Police ID Suspect in Fatal Michigan Shootings] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/latest-police-id-suspect-fatal-michigan-shootings-37093030 |date=20160221183345 }}, [[ABC_News|ABC News]], February 21, 2016</ref>。

== 受害者 ==
第一個受害者為泰勒·D·史密斯<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.mlive.com/news/kalamazoo/index.ssf/2016/02/mattawan_high_school_senior_a.html |title= High School Senior from Mattawan Killed in Kalamazoo Mass Shootings |date= February 21, 2016 |work= MLive |first= Emily |last= Monacelli |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303042332/http://www.mlive.com/news/kalamazoo/index.ssf/2016/02/mattawan_high_school_senior_a.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.abc10.com/news/local/kalamazoo-vigil-to-honor-shooting-victims/50019721 |location= Walker, MI |publisher= WZZM-TV |date= February 21, 2016 |title= Kalamazoo Vigil Honoring Shooting Victims |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160302051813/http://www.abc10.com/news/local/kalamazoo-vigil-to-honor-shooting-victims/50019721 |dead-url= no }}</ref>（Tyler D. Smith，17歲）及其父親理查德·E·史密斯（Richard E. Smith，53歲），兩人皆於起亞汽車經銷商中被殺害<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.buzzfeed.com/claudiakoerner/these-are-the-victims-of-the-kalamazoo-michigan-shootings#.mr4xzD6eQW |title= These Are the Victims of the Kalamazoo, Michigan Shootings |first= Claudia |last= Koerner |work= Buzzfeed |date= February 21, 2016 |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160301135325/http://www.buzzfeed.com/claudiakoerner/these-are-the-victims-of-the-kalamazoo-michigan-shootings#.mr4xzD6eQW |dead-url= no }}</ref>。另外四名女子分別是瑪麗·喬·奈<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.freep.com/story/news/local/michigan/2016/02/21/kalamazoo-victim-retired-teacher/80702118/ |title= One Kalamazoo Victim a Battle Creek Retired Teacher |work= Detroit Free Press |date= February 21, 2016 |first= Jennifer |last= Bowman |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160302212214/http://www.freep.com/story/news/local/michigan/2016/02/21/kalamazoo-victim-retired-teacher/80702118/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>（Mary Jo Nye，60歲）、瑪麗·盧·奈<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.vox.com/2016/2/21/11081818/kalamazoo-michigan-shootings-jason-brian-dalton |work= Vox |date= February 21, 2016 |title= Kalamazoo, Michigan, Shootings: What We Know |first= German |last= Lopez |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195340/http://www.vox.com/2016/2/21/11081818/kalamazoo-michigan-shootings-jason-brian-dalton |dead-url= no }}</ref>（Mary Lou Nye，62歲）、多蘿西·布朗<ref>{{cite press release |url= http://www.michigan.gov/msp/0,4643,7-123-58995_72487-377378--,00.html |title= Kalamazoo Shooting Update |publisher= Michigan State Police |date= February 21, 2016 |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303073509/http://www.michigan.gov/msp/0,4643,7-123-58995_72487-377378--,00.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>（Dorothy Brown，74歲）以及芭芭拉·霍桑<ref>{{cite news |url= http://fox17online.com/2016/02/21/victims-kalamazoo-shooting/ |title= What We Know So Far: Kalamazoo Shooting Victims |first= Bob |last= Brenzing |location= Grand Rapids, MI |publisher= WXMI-TV |date= February 21, 2016 |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-03-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305160533/http://fox17online.com/2016/02/21/victims-kalamazoo-shooting/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>（Barbara Hawthorne，68歲）皆於餅乾桶餐廳（Cracker Barrel）中被殺害。當時在餅乾桶餐廳與四名女子在一起的14歲女孩阿碧潔爾·科普夫（Abigail Kopf），其頭部被子彈射中<ref name=battlecreekenquirer>{{cite web|url=http://www.battlecreekenquirer.com/story/news/local/2016/02/22/parents-abigail-kopf-she-did-not-deserve/80779376/|title=Parents of Abigail Kopf: 'She did not deserve this'|first=Jennifer|last=Bowman|work=Battle Creek Enquirer|date=February 24, 2016|accessdate=February 25, 2016}}</ref>，起初判定為死亡，但後來被確認尚有生命跡象<ref name="woodtv-police-id"/><ref name="rt">{{cite news |title= 6 Killed, 2 Injured, in Kalamazoo Shooting Spree as Driver Targets 'Random' Victims |url= https://www.rt.com/usa/333151-michigan-random-shooting-victims/ |work= [[Russia_Today|Russia Today]] |date= February 21, 2016 |accessdate= February 21, 2016 |archive-date= 2016-02-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160221080953/https://www.rt.com/usa/333151-michigan-random-shooting-victims/ |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。截至2月23日，她呼吸時仍然依靠呼吸機，情況並不樂觀；2月28日，她已能夠自主呼吸<ref name=battlecreekenquirer/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ajc.com/news/news/national/14-year-old-kalamazoo-shooting-victims-condition-i/nqZb4/ |publisher=''Atlanta Journal-Constitution'' |date=February 28, 2016 |title=14-year-old Kalamazoo shooting victim's condition improves |accessdate=February 28, 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303005251/http://www.ajc.com/news/news/national/14-year-old-kalamazoo-shooting-victims-condition-i/nqZb4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

